---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const samples = [
  {
    slug: 'pr-review',
    title: 'pr-review',
    description:
      'Automated pull request review built as structured Claude skills. Drop-in GitHub Actions workflow plus five review skills (correctness, test adequacy, design fit, readability, breaking-change impact).',
    series: '3-part blog series',
    href: '/samples/#pr-review',
    blog: 'https://tech.bdigitalmedia.io/blog/designing-ai-pr-review-claude-skills',
  },
];
---

<Layout title="bdigital.public · code samples from the engineering blog">
  <section class="container-inner">
    <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-wider">bdigital public</p>
    <h1 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-snow mt-3 tracking-tight">
      code samples from the engineering blog, generalized for reuse
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-zinc-400 mt-6 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
      Each sample is extracted from a real project, stripped of proprietary
      context, and sized to be useful on its own. Pair a sample with the blog
      post it ships with for the full walkthrough.
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-8">
      <a
        href="https://tech.bdigitalmedia.io"
        class="no-underline bg-snow text-obsidian font-medium px-5 py-2.5 rounded-sm hover:bg-zinc-200 transition-colors"
      >
        read the blog
      </a>
      <a
        href="/samples/"
        class="no-underline border border-zinc-700 text-zinc-200 font-medium px-5 py-2.5 rounded-sm hover:border-zinc-500 hover:text-snow transition-colors"
      >
        browse samples
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container-inner mt-20">
    <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-snow mb-8">
      featured sample
    </h2>
    <ul class="space-y-6">
      {samples.map((s) => (
        <li class="border border-zinc-900 rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-zinc-700 transition-colors">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-xs text-zinc-500 mb-3">
            <span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-zinc-900 text-zinc-400 rounded-sm">sample</span>
            <span>{s.series}</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-snow">
            <a href={s.href} class="no-underline hover:text-zinc-300">{s.title}</a>
          </h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-400 mt-3 leading-relaxed">{s.description}</p>
          <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-x-5 gap-y-2 text-sm">
            <a href={s.href} class="no-underline text-zinc-300 hover:text-snow">view sample →</a>
            <a href={s.blog} class="no-underline text-zinc-500 hover:text-zinc-300">related blog post →</a>
          </div>
        </li>
      ))}
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="container-inner mt-20">
    <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-snow mb-6">
      how to use this repo
    </h2>
    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-zinc max-w-none">
      <ol class="text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
        <li>Pick a sample that matches the blog post you are reading.</li>
        <li>
          Copy the sample directory into your own repository, or clone this one
          and modify in place. Every sample is self-contained.
        </li>
        <li>
          Read the sample's <code>README.md</code> for required secrets,
          permissions, and customization points.
        </li>
        <li>
          For the <code>pr-review</code> sample, set an
          <code>ANTHROPIC_API_KEY</code> repo secret and ensure the workflow
          has <code>pull-requests: write</code> permission.
        </li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container-inner mt-20">
    <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-snow mb-6">
      contributing
    </h2>
    <p class="text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
      New samples are welcome. Each should pair with a blog post, be free of
      proprietary context, and follow the open-source structure laid out in
      <a href="https://github.com/neurot1cal/bdigital-public/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md" class="text-zinc-200">
        CONTRIBUTING.md
      </a>
      . Bug reports and generalization PRs are also welcome.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
